# HTML Conventions

## Structure

- Single `index.html` serves the entire portfolio
- `lang="ru"` — all user-facing text in Russian
- Semantic sections: `<main>`, `<section>`, `<header>`, `<footer>`
- Sections have `id` attributes for navigation scroll-spy
- `data-scroll="start|center"` attribute controls scroll-to positioning

## Assets

- Images: `/images/` (icons, logos, cases, screenshots)
- Fonts: `/fonts/inter/` (regular, semibold, variable)
- Documents: root of `public/`
- Base path `/portfolio` in production (Vite `base` config)

## Inline Styles

- Critical CSS for preloader is inlined in `<style>` tag in `<head>`
- CSS variables for theme colors defined on `:root`
- Body has `overflow: hidden` until JS removes it (preloader pattern)
